```java
package MonkeyPatch;

import java.lang.instrument.ClassFileTransformer;
import java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets;
import java.security.ProtectionDomain;
import java.util.Arrays;
import java.util.regex.Pattern;
import java.util.regex.Matcher;
import javax.xml.bind.DatatypeConverter;


public class PatchBurpSuite implements ClassFileTransformer {
    public byte[] transform(ClassLoader loader, String className, Class<?> classBeingRedefined, ProtectionDomain protectionDomain, byte[] classfileBuffer) {
        String d = DatatypeConverter.printHexBinary(classfileBuffer);
        byte[] baKeyword = new byte[d.length() / 2];
        for(int i = 0; i < baKeyword.length; ++i) {
            baKeyword[i] = (byte)(255 & Integer.parseInt(d.substring(i * 2, i * 2 + 2), 16));
        }
        d = new String(baKeyword, StandardCharsets.UTF_8);
        if (!d.contains("751a8be34c1a9ed9633d04be3ba075a7")) {
            return null;
        }
        byte[] newBuffer = new byte[classfileBuffer.length];
        System.arraycopy(classfileBuffer, 0, newBuffer, 0, newBuffer.length);
        String key_all = Arrays.toString(newBuffer);
        Pattern p = Pattern.compile("90, .\\w+, -89, 0, 4, -65, 25, 5, 21, 6, 5, 100, 51, 28, -102, 0, 18, -89, 0, 4, -65, 16, 61, -89, 0, 4, -65, -96, 90, .\\w+, 21, 9, -68, 8, 58, 10, 3, 54, 11, 21, 11, 21, 9, -94, 0, 31, 25, 10, 28, -102, 0, 29, 21, 11, 25, 5, 21, 8, 21, 11, 96, 51, 84, -124, 11, 1, 28, -103, -1, -28, -89, 0, 4, -65, 21, 8, -68, 8, 58, 7, 3, 54, 11, 21, 11, 21, 8, -94, 0, 28, 25, 7, 21, 11, 25, 5, 21, 11, 51, 84, -124, 11, 1, 28, -102, 0, 14, 28, -103, -1, -25, -89, 0, 4, -65");
        Matcher m = p.matcher(key_all);
        if (!m.find()) {
            return null;
        }
        String[] key_sp = key_all.substring(0, m.start()).split(", ");
        Pattern p2 = Pattern.compile(", 21, 9, -68, 8, 58, 10, 3, 54, 11, 21, 11, 21, 9, -94, 0, 31, 25, 10, 28, -102, 0, 29, 21, 11, 25, 5, 21, 8, 21, 11, 96, 51, 84, -124, 11, 1, 28, -103, -1, -28, -89, 0, 4, -65, 21, 8, -68, 8, 58, 7, 3, 54, 11, 21, 11, 21, 8, -94, 0, 28, 25, 7, 21, 11, 25, 5, 21, 11, 51, 84, -124, 11, 1, 28, -102, 0, 14, 28, -103, -1, -25, -89, 0, 4, -65");
        Matcher m2 = p2.matcher(key_all);
        if (!m2.find()) {
            return null;
        }
        String[] key_sp2 = key_all.substring(0, m2.start()).split(", ");
        int[] patch = new int[]{key_sp.length, 0, key_sp.length + 1, 3, key_sp.length + 28, 0, key_sp.length + 29, 3, key_sp.length + 115, 167, key_sp.length + 116, 90, key_sp.length + 117, 39 + newBuffer[key_sp2.length - 1] - 117};
        for (int i = 0; i < patch.length; i += 2) {
            newBuffer[patch[i]] = (byte) patch[i + 1];
        }
        return newBuffer;
    }
}
```

* 14-22Ë°åÂØπclassfileBufferËøõË°åÂà§Êñ≠ÔºåÊâæÂà∞ÈúÄË¶ÅÂä®ÊÄÅpatchÁöÑclass
* 23-37Ë°åËÆ°ÁÆóÈúÄË¶Å‰øÆÊîπÁöÑ7‰∏™patch‰ΩçÁΩÆ
* 38-42Ë°åÂØπclassfileBufferËøõË°å‰øÆÊîπ
